// ================================================================
// MANAGER.IO CONTEXT HANDSHAKE
// Works with BOTH Cloud Edition and Desktop Edition.
// Cloud:   apiEndpoint = https://xxx.manager.io
// Desktop: apiEndpoint = http://localhost:5000
// Auth ALWAYS received via postMessage — token NEVER hardcoded.
// n-Law 03: Zero vendor lock-in. n-Law 04: Full audit trail.
